	   <tr><td colspan=2>I left a long and very detailed post Jan 5 6AM, about lower level strategy for SKs when dueling, and also some good advice when fighting mobs, yet some people gave me an &quot;awful&quot; rating, but did not leave any feedback as to why.<br><br>If you disagree with my strategy, thats fine, but if your going to give an &quot;awful&quot; rating then at least have the courtesy to leave feedback as to why you disagree, and perhaps your own strategy.<br><br>To read my earlier post, you will have to change the default filter to never filter, which I always do anyway, because I'm interested in hearing what everybody has to say.  If the people who left an &quot;awful&quot; rating for my first post are reading this, I would appreciate it if they left feedback.  And if anyone reads it and wether they agree with it or not, but think the post was good, please give a positive rating.<br><br>For the record, for anyone who disagrees with the strategy previously posted, I use this strategy and it works very effectively for me.  I will accept a duel from anyone within 3 levels of me on Brell Serelis, name is Kallirye and I'm usually on between 3-10pm pacific.<br>&nbsp;<br>Daughter of Hate, Shadow Knight of TheDead, Dedicated of Innoruuk, Consort of Emperor Crush.</td></tr>
