	   <tr><td colspan=2>When PvP'ing any pet class, the worst thing you could do is engage their pet! That's what they would like you to do, go after the necro, ignore his pet. The more time you spend with his pet the more time he has to fear you, root you, and let you rot.<br>I'd open up with Harm Touch, then fear the Necro, then snare him/her, then beat the tar outta him/her.<br>The Necro will try to get away, if he's at all smart, by using Shadow Step, so keep him/her feared so they can't!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
